3. PLANE CRASH AND TRAIN COLLISIONS (PSO 330, 331)

Aircraft Accidents - Procedure

PSO-330:

On the occurrence of an aircraft accident, the Village Secretary, or
Panchayat Executive Officer should report the matter to the nearest (i)
Magistrate and (ii) Police Station or outpost. If any person is injured as a
result of the accident, report the matter to the nearest medical Officer.
